## Directory Enumeration (Gobuster)

### Objective
Discover hidden directories and endpoints on a web application.

### Tool Used
- Gobuster

### Command Used
gobuster dir -u http://localhost:3000 -w common.txt

### Findings
- Identified multiple endpoints such as /assets and /rest
- Some endpoints returned restricted access (403)
- Demonstrates presence of hidden server-side routes

### Security Insight
Hidden endpoints may expose sensitive functionality if not properly secured.

### Skills Demonstrated
- Directory enumeration
- Endpoint discovery
- Web attack surface mappin
